			<div id="post-7261" class="post-7261 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-fruit tag-gardening tag-interviews tag-lee-reich tag-orchard tag-permaculture">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/reich-growing-fruit-naturally" title="Permalink to Episode-971- Dr. Lee Reich on Growing Fruit Naturally" rel="bookmark">Episode-971- Dr. Lee Reich on Growing Fruit Naturally</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/reich-growing-fruit-naturally" title="11:59 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">August 30, 2012</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/reich-growing-fruit-naturally#comments" title="Comment on Episode-971- Dr. Lee Reich on Growing Fruit Naturally">26 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<div id="tweetbutton7261" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Freich-growing-fruit-naturally&amp;text=Episode-971-%20Dr.%20Lee%20Reich%20on%20Growing%20Fruit%20Naturally&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Freich-growing-fruit-naturally" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
