<div class="podPress_downloadlinks podPress_downloadlinks_audio_mp3"><a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00971-lee-reich-on-growing-fruit-naturally.mp3" target="new" title="Download: Episode-971- Dr. Lee Reich on Growing Fruit Naturally" class="podpress_downloadimglink podpress_downloadimglink_audio_mp3"><img src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/audio_mp3_button.png" class="podPress_imgicon podpress_imgicon_audio_mp3" alt="" /></a> <span class="podpress_mediafile_title podpress_mediafile_title_audio_mp3">Episode-971- Dr. Lee Reich on Growing Fruit Naturally</span> <span class="podpress_mediafile_dursize podpress_mediafile_dursize_audio_mp3">[ 54:14 ]</span> <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_2" class="podpress_playlink podpress_playlink_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressShowHidePlayer('2', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00971-lee-reich-on-growing-fruit-naturally.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-971- Dr. Lee Reich on Growing Fruit Naturally', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;"><span id="podPressPlayerSpace_2_PlayLink" class="podPress_playerspace_playlink">Play Now</span></a><input type="hidden" id="podPressPlayerSpace_2_OrigURL" value="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00971-lee-reich-on-growing-fruit-naturally.mp3" /> | <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_2" class="podpress_playinpopup podpress_playinpopup_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressPopupPlayer('2', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00971-lee-reich-on-growing-fruit-naturally.mp3', 290, 24, 'The Survival Podcast', '7261', 'Episode-971- Dr. Lee Reich on Growing Fruit Naturally', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;">Play in Popup</a> | <a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00971-lee-reich-on-growing-fruit-naturally.mp3" target="new" class="podpress_downloadlink podpress_download