<li><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/forum" target="_blank">Join Our Forum</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/be-a-part-of-episode-1000-and-revolution-2-0" target="_blank">Be Part of Episode 1000</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/jack-spirko-to-present-at-the-self-reliance-expo-in-hickory-nc">Meet Jack at the Hickory, NC Self Reliance Expo</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.shelfreliance.com/podcast" target="_blank">ShelfReliance.com</a> – (sponsor of the day)</li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.silverandgoldshop.com/" target="_blank">Silver and Gold Shop</a> – (sponsor of the day)</li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://urbanfarmandbeehives.com/" target="_blank">Urban Farm and Beehives</a> &#8211; (Mil&#8217;s Site)</li>
