			<div id="post-7219" class="post-7219 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-blog tag-msb-updates">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/three-new-msb-discounts-for-brigade-members" title="Permalink to Three New MSB Discounts for Brigade Members" rel="bookmark">Three New MSB Discounts for Brigade Members</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/three-new-msb-discounts-for-brigade-members" title="1:21 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">August 23, 2012</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/three-new-msb-discounts-for-brigade-members#comments" title="Comment on Three New MSB Discounts for Brigade Members">4 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<div id="tweetbutton7219" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fthree-new-msb-discounts-for-brigade-members&amp;text=Three%20New%20MSB%20Discounts%20for%20Brigade%20Members&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fthree-new-msb-discounts-for-brigade-members" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><p>I am constantly working to improve the value of the MSB, to that end I have three new MSB discounts to announce.  One is a new improved discount from a long term sponsor and supporter and two are brand new.  The big news is two of them will allow you to get discounts on silver and gold.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong><span style="color: #800000;">Silver and Gold Shop</span></strong> &#8211; has expanded its discount program and now offers a $.50 discount per coin on all 1 oz. generic silver bullion rounds:  Buffalo, Morgan, Walking Liberty, Civil War, Divisible Prospectors, 1804.  They are also offering discounts on Tea Party Silver Rounds with larger orders.  To see their full selection visit <a target="_blank" href="http://www.silverandgoldshop.com/" target="_blank">www.silverandgoldshop.com </a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong><span style="color: #800000;">NoDak Arms</span> </strong>– Offers all MSB members 5% off all in stock NoDak Arms Ammo.  They also offer reloading of YOUR used brass for 10% off our ammo list cost (minimum 500rd count). At this time we do not offer online purchasing so orders must be called in by phone. To see all of their great deals visit <a target="_blank" href="http://www.nodakarms.com/" target="_blank"> www.nodakarms.com</a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong><span style="color: #800000;">JM Bullion</span></strong> &#8211; is an online website that supplies individual investors with physical gold and silver products at the lowest prices possible.  They deal strictly in physical metals intended for delivery directly to the customer.  They offer an exclusive MSB discount on larger orders of gold and silver bullion.  They offer $5 off  any order of $300 or more and  $10 off any order of $1000 or more.  To order visit <a target="_blank" href="http://www.jmbullion.com" target="_blank">www.jmbullion.com</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Full details including the codes for these discounts are now on the benefits page of the MSB.  For those that may see the precious metals discounts as somewhat small please understand that margins on metals are very thin, I have worked hard for a long time to get you guys these types of deals and it wasn&#8217;t easy.</p>
<p>With the Silver and Gold Shop discount you can get discounts on smaller purchases including just a few coins.  The the JM Bullion discount when you add it to their already low prices it makes purchases in the 300 dollar and up range very tough to beat.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://bittip.it/" class="bittip-button" default-amount=".002" request="count" url="" donation-message="" donation-address="1J7bQzw5g71P3BUmnToZePdh7CrBjdtTKc"></a></p><script>(function() {var s = document.createElement('script');var t = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];s.type = 'text/javascript';s.async = true;var url; if (window.location.protocol == 'https:'){url = 'https://bitcoinsberlin.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/button-loader.js'} else { url = 'http://bittip.it/cdn/button-loader.js';};s.src = url;t.parentNode.insertBefore(s, t);})();</script>							</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
