			<div id="post-7190" class="post-7190 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-ben-falk tag-business tag-heating tag-permaculture tag-wood-stove">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/falk-of-whole-systems-design" title="Permalink to Episode-964- Ben Falk of Whole Systems Design" rel="bookmark">Episode-964- Ben Falk of Whole Systems Design</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/falk-of-whole-systems-design" title="7:00 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">August 21, 2012</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/falk-of-whole-systems-design#comments" title="Comment on Episode-964- Ben Falk of Whole Systems Design">19 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<div id="tweetbutton7190" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Ffalk-of-whole-systems-design&amp;text=Episode-964-%20Ben%20Falk%20of%20Whole%20Systems%20Design&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Ffalk-of-whole-systems-design" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
<div class="podpress_playerspace podpress_playerspace_audio_mp3 podpress_mp3player" style="display:block;" ><div id="podPressPlayerSpace_9"><!-- podPress --></div></div>
<div class="podPress_downloadlinks podPress_downloadlinks_audio_mp3"><a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00964-ben-cook-of-whole-systems-design.mp3" target="new" title="Download: Episode-964- Ben Falk of Whole Systems Design" class="podpress_downloadimglink podpress_downloadimglink_audio_mp3"><img src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/audio_mp3_button.png" class="podPress_imgicon podpress_imgicon_audio_mp3" alt="" /></a> <span class="podpress_mediafile_title podpress_mediafile_title_audio_mp3">Episode-964- Ben Falk of Whole Systems Design</span> <span class="podpress_mediafile_dursize podpress_mediafile_dursize_audio_mp3">[ 1:00:43 ]</span> <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_9" class="podpress_playlink podpress_playlink_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressShowHidePlayer('9', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00964-ben-cook-of-whole-systems-design.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-964- Ben Falk of Whole Systems Design', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;"><span id="podPressPlayerSpace_9_PlayLink" class="podPress_playerspace_playlink">Play Now</span></a><input type="hidden" id="podPressPlayerSpace_9_OrigURL" value="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00964-ben-cook-of-whole-systems-design.mp3" /> | <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_9" class="podpress_playinpopup podpress_playinpopup_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressPopupPlayer('9', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00964-ben-cook-of-whole-systems-design.mp3', 290, 24, 'The Survival Podcast', '7190', 'Episode-964- Ben Falk of Whole Systems Design', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;">Play in Popup</a> | <a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00964-ben-cook-of-whole-systems-design.mp3" target="new" class="podpress_downloadlink podpress_downloadlink_audio_mp3">Download</a></div></div>
<script type="text/javascript">podPressShowHidePlayer('9', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00964-ben-cook-of-whole-systems-design.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-964- Ben Falk of Whole Systems Design', 'The Survival Podcast');</script><div id="attachment_5462" style="width: 210px" class="wp-caption alignleft"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.wholesystemsdesign.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-5462" title="Ben Falk of WholeSystemsDesign.com" src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/benfalk.jpg" alt="Ben Falk of WholeSystemsDesign.com" width="200" height="184" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Ben Falk of WholeSystemsDesign.com</p></div>
<p>Ben Falk developed Whole Systems Design, as a land-based response to biological and cultural extinction and the increasing separation between people and elemental things. Life as a designer, builder, ecologist, tree-tender, and back country traveler continually informs Ben’s integrative approach to developing landscapes and buildings.</p>
<p>His home landscape and the WSD studio site in Vermont&#8217;s Mad River Valley serve as a proving ground for the innovative land developments featured in the projects of Whole Systems Design. Ben has studied architecture and landscape architecture at the graduate level and holds a master’s degree in land-use planning and design.</p>
<p>He has taught design courses at the University of Vermont and Harvard’s Arnold Arboretum as well as on permaculture design, microclimate design, and design for climate change. He serves on the Board of Directors and Faculty at the Yestermorrow Design-Build School.  Ben joins us today to discuss developing a permaculture homestead and creating a permaculture design business.</p>
<p><strong> <span style="color: #800000;">Additional Resources for Today’s Show</span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/members" target="_blank">Members Support Brigade</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tspcopper.com/" target="_blank">TSP Copper</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.harvesteating.com" target="_blank">Harvest Eating</a> – (sponsor of the day)</li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.freestateproject.org" target="_blank">Free State Project</a> – (sponsor of the day)</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<strong><span style="color: #800000;">Ben&#8217;s Links</span></strong></p>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.wholesystemsdesign.com" target="_blank">WholeSystemsDesign.com</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.wholesystemsdesign.com/projects/whole-systems-research-farm-mad-river-valley-vt/">Photos of Whole Systems Design Site Location</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.wholesystemsdesign.com/whole-systems-skills" target="_blank">Workshops at Whole Systems Design</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.wholesystemsdesign.com/permaculture-design-course/" target="_blank">Info on the Whole Systems Design PDC</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Whole-Systems-Design-LLC/103407076363918?ref=ts" target="_blank">Whole Systems Design on Facebook</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://twitter.com/WholeSystemDes" target="_blank">Whole Systems Design on Twitter</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/user/WholeSystemsDesign" target="_blank">Whole Systems Design on YouTube</a></li>
</ul>
</ul>
